text: import java.net.*; import java.io.*; class WebPage { public static void main(String [] args ){ try { URL u = new URL("http://www.dit.ie"); InputStream in = u.openStream() ; int c; while ((c = in.read()) '= -1) System.out.write(c) ; in.close() ; } catch (Exception ex) { System.err.println(ex) ; } } }
